---
title: Smart Mexican Shrimp Skillet with Avocado Salsa
description: Tonight's skillet dinner is packed with delights, from Mexican-style spices and fresh cilantro to creamy avocado salsa! A pepper and zucchini hash rounds it all out for a delicious yet light meal.

